column5: Looks like a PERFECT day too Bud.
I only got 2 days a week to get my fun in.  Well, 3 this one. LOL
I am so jealous of you.  lol Nice fish too Mr B
The China bowl is calling you!!! Haven't seen Hippie Bob yet though!! (in joke, folks)

I have seen him the past couple of weeks at timmies here. 5am. he is renoing his basement.  I will not be up that way til Oct. China bowl will be no more. Huge mansion being built on the land. Ya  I can walk down or toon down, but there are so many other spots to fish..
